title: Syllabus mentioned in ERP
text: Tests on bitumen, emulsion, cutback, soil and aggregates, aggregate blending, viscosity of binders, Bituminous mix design, visco-elastic properties of bituminous mixtures, tests on modified binders, speed, headway and travel time studies on highways, Parking surveys.
